text: Calum Worthy (born January 28, 1991) is a Canadian actor, writer, and producer. He played Dez on the Disney Channel series Austin & Ally, Alex Trimboli in the Netflix series American Vandal, Nicholas Godejohn in the Hulu series The Act, and himself in The Coppertop Flop Show. ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian movie actors Category:Canadian television actors Category:Canadian voice actors Category:Canadian television writers Category:Canadian television producers Category:Actors from Vancouver Category:Writers from British Columbia
